java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable, Operable, Realtime, Representable, java.io.Serializable
public class ElectricResistance
extends Quantity

This class represents an Electric Resistance. The system unit for this quantity is "m²·kg/(s³·A²)". By default, instances of this class are showed in Ohm ("Ohm").

4.1, February 10, 2003
